                            <article class="bg-content p-3 rounded mt-3">
                                <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-3">What Is HER TREES?</h2>
                                <p><strong>HER TREES: PUZZLE DREAM</strong> is a point-and-click puzzle game set inside
                                    a surreal, dreamlike world. Players explore mysterious rooms, move and combine
                                    objects, and uncover the hidden logic behind each puzzle to progress through the
                                    story.</p>
                                <p><strong>HER TREES</strong> features entirely monochrome, hand-drawn visuals and a
                                    minimalist artistic style. The atmospheric environment and subtle animations create
                                    a
                                    quiet, slightly eerie mood that complements every puzzle. As a non-verbal game, HER
                                    TREES requires no reading, no sound-based puzzles, and no color recognition, making
                                    it accessible to a wide range of players worldwide.</p>
                                <p>This is the third game in the HER TREES series, following <a href="/her-trees-first-puzzle">HER TREES: First Puzzle</a>
                                    and <a href="/her-trees-the-puzzle-house">HER TREES: THE PUZZLE HOUSE</a>. While PUZZLE DREAM works perfectly as a
                                    standalone title, fans who enjoy it can also explore the two previous entries for
                                    more puzzles and story. First Puzzle is where the journey begins — a
                                    great starting point for anyone who wants to experience the series from the very
                                    first chapter. THE PUZZLE HOUSE expands on the original with more complex
                                    puzzles and deeper environmental storytelling. Together, all three titles
                                    offer a complete and rewarding puzzle experience.</p>
                                <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-3">How It Works</h2>
                                <p>In HER TREES, players interact with the environment by clicking on objects, dragging
                                    them to new locations, and combining items to trigger mechanisms or reveal hidden
                                    clues. There are no tedious calculations or note-taking required. Every puzzle is
                                    designed to be solved through intuition and careful observation.</p>
                                <p>Stuck on a tricky room? Built-in hints and full solutions become
                                    available after a certain amount of time, so you can always keep moving forward.</p>
                            </article>
                            <div class="post-features mt-3">
                                <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-3">Features</h2>
                                <div class="row g-3">
                                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                                        <div class="bg-content p-3 rounded">
                                            <h3 class="fs-6 fw-bold">40+ Unique Puzzles</h3>
                                            <p class="m-0 mt-1">HER TREES: PUZZLE DREAM contains over 40 original
                                                puzzles. Each one introduces a different concept, and the difficulty
                                                increases gradually as you progress. No two challenges feel the same.
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                                        <div class="bg-content p-3 rounded">
                                            <h3 class="fs-6 fw-bold">Built-In Hints &amp; Solutions</h3>
                                            <p class="m-0 mt-1">Stuck on a puzzle? Optional hints and
                                                complete solutions unlock after a set amount of time. You control
                                                the pace of your experience — no pressure, no frustration.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                                        <div class="bg-content p-3 rounded">
                                            <h3 class="fs-6 fw-bold">1.5 – 3 Hours of Playtime</h3>
                                            <p class="m-0 mt-1">Expect a compact, focused journey. A full
                                                playthrough takes approximately 1.5 to 3 hours — ideal for a single
                                                sitting or a few short sessions.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                                        <div class="bg-content p-3 rounded">
                                            <h3 class="fs-6 fw-bold">Fully Accessible Design</h3>
                                            <p class="m-0 mt-1">HER TREES is a non-verbal game with an entirely
                                                monochrome art style. No puzzles rely on color perception or sound, so
                                                players of all backgrounds and abilities can enjoy every moment without
                                                barriers.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                                        <div class="bg-content p-3 rounded">
                                            <h3 class="fs-6 fw-bold">Hand-Drawn Monochrome Art</h3>
