                                <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-3">FAQs</h2>
                                <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-3">
                                    <div class="bg-content p-3 rounded">
                                        <h3 class="fs-6 fw-bold">Do I need to play previous HER TREES games
                                            first?</h3>
                                        <p class="m-0 mt-1">No. HER TREES: PUZZLE DREAM is the third game in the
                                            series, but it is designed as a standalone title. You can jump right in
                                            without any prior experience. However, if you'd like the full story,
                                            begin with First Puzzle and then play THE PUZZLE HOUSE before starting
                                            PUZZLE DREAM.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="bg-content p-3 rounded">
                                        <h3 class="fs-6 fw-bold">How long does HER TREES take to complete?</h3>
                                        <p class="m-0 mt-1">A full playthrough takes
                                            approximately 1.5 to 3 hours, depending on your puzzle-solving speed. Some
                                            breeze through it; others prefer to linger and explore.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="bg-content p-3 rounded">
                                        <h3 class="fs-6 fw-bold">Is HER TREES suitable for beginners?</h3>
                                        <p class="m-0 mt-1">Absolutely. The puzzles are intuitive and require no
                                            special knowledge. Built-in hints are available whenever you need them. Both
                                            experienced puzzle players and newcomers will find something to enjoy. If
                                            you're new
                                            to the series, First Puzzle offers a gentler learning curve as an entry
                                            point.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="bg-content p-3 rounded">
                                        <h3 class="fs-6 fw-bold">Are there any text or language requirements
                                            in HER TREES?</h3>
                                        <p class="m-0 mt-1">None at all. HER TREES is a completely non-verbal game.
                                            There is no
                                            written or spoken language, so players from any region can enjoy it
                                            without a language barrier.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="bg-content p-3 rounded">
                                        <h3 class="fs-6 fw-bold">Can colorblind players enjoy HER TREES?</h3>
                                        <p class="m-0 mt-1">Yes. The entirely monochrome design means no
                                            puzzle relies on color recognition. Players with any form of color vision
                                            deficiency can play without limitations.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="bg-content p-3 rounded">
                                        <h3 class="fs-6 fw-bold">Does HER TREES require sound to play?</h3>
                                        <p class="m-0 mt-1">Not at all. No puzzles depend on audio cues. You can
                                            play with or without sound — the experience remains fully intact either way.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="bg-content p-3 rounded">
                                        <h3 class="fs-6 fw-bold">Are there hints available in HER TREES?</h3>
                                        <p class="m-0 mt-1">Yes. Both hints and full solutions are provided for
                                            every puzzle. They become available after a certain amount of time, so you
                                            can choose when — or whether — to use them.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="bg-content p-3 rounded">
                                        <h3 class="fs-6 fw-bold">Does HER TREES contain ads?</h3>
                                        <p class="m-0 mt-1">No. The experience is completely ad-free — an
                                            uninterrupted journey from the first room to the last.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="bg-content p-3 rounded">
                                        <h3 class="fs-6 fw-bold">What other games are in the HER TREES series?</h3>
                                        <p class="m-0 mt-1">The HER TREES series includes three titles: First Puzzle,
                                            THE PUZZLE HOUSE, and PUZZLE DREAM. Each game can be
                                            enjoyed independently, but playing all three delivers the complete
                                            experience — with progressively deeper puzzles and storytelling.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="bg-content p-3 rounded">
                                        <h3 class="fs-6 fw-bold">What platform is HER TREES available on?</h3>
                                        <p class="m-0 mt-1">The game uses simple mouse-based point-and-click controls.
                                            Check the official store page for current platform availability.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="bg-content p-3 rounded">
                                        <h3 class="fs-6 fw-bold">What type of game is HER TREES?</h3>
                                        <p class="m-0 mt-1">HER TREES: PUZZLE DREAM is a single-player point-and-click
                                            puzzle and adventure game with escape-room-style mechanics, environmental
                                            storytelling, and hand-drawn monochrome visuals.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
